QuestData.Title: Glimmering Sigil of Whirlaxis
QuestData.Description: The sigils of the Abyssal High Council are crafted from the distilled essence of the element of their holder. This sigil was carved with biting winds.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Glimmering Sigil of Whirlaxis to Field Marshal Snowfall in Silithus.
